data.description: This home is located on a large corner lot within walking distance to the city park, football field, Firefly Stage.  This is a 4-bedroom 2 bath home with lots of space to entertain for gatherings, open concept for kitchen dining and living room in this great space, which is the focal point, this space places 2 bedrooms on each end of the home, bedrooms are very spacious. Large, covered patio to watch your favorite games with friends while the steaks are on the grill. Large picture window in the living room to watch the kids in the back yard and to let in a lot of light. The kitchen space can have a movable island or coffee bar to gather around while entertaining.  This home doesn't have any wasted space.  This is a must to see make your appt today. VERY MOTIVATED SELLER
